    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🏰 One world. One winner. Then it all begins again.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquest! is a persistent multiplayer strategy game where players battle in a live, shared world — until one emerges victorious. Born on IRC in 1993, rebuilt for modern platforms, it’s fast, brutal, and unforgiving.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕒 <strong>Instant command resolution</strong> — no waiting, no fluff<br>🌍 <strong>Persistent world</strong> — all players affect a single, shared game<br>⚔️ <strong>Wage war across 3 distinct regions</strong> in every Age <br>👑 <strong>The world resets only when a player wins</strong> — can you survive to the end?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There’s no base-building. No animations. No filler. Just raw strategy and a world that never resets... until someone conquers it all. </p>",
